    <h2 id="shipping">Shipping</h2>

    <p>For shipping, the following rules apply:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>We generally ship in 1 to 3 business days</li>
      <li>We ship to The Netherlands, Germany, Belgium, Austria, Denmark, France, Luxembourg.</li>
      <li>Shipping costs:
        <ul>
          <li>Netherlands: €5,99, free shipping from €75,-</li>
          <li>Austria, Belgium, Denmark, France, Germany, Luxembourg: €8,99, free shipping from €100,-</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>Please note that at the current time, all courier companies including PostNL are very busy so there could be a delay. But if your track &amp; trace has not changed for over five working days, please contact us immediately at webshop@folkingebrew.nl. We have a 30 day time window at PostNL for starting an investigation. After that refunds are not possible!</p>

    <h2 id="returning">Returning</h2>

    <p>You have the right to return your package for a period of 14 days after the purchase. The costs for returning the package are yours. In order to return your beers and/or other products, please send an email to webshop@folkingebrew.nl. We’ll send you instructions. If we received and checked your return shipment, you will be refunded for the beers and/or other products you returned.</p>

    <h2 id="contact">Contact</h2>

    <p>You can contact us with any question through our <a href="/contact/">contact form</a>.</p>
